rg/abs/2607.08576","score":95,"stars":5,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"gravitational lens modelling","points":28}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Other Selected Research"]},{"id":"2607.08286","canonical_id":"2607.08286","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Lambda as a Probe of Lensing Consistency","authors":["Yuan Shi","Li Cui","Carlo Giocoli"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO","astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"本文提出了一个框架，通过引入空间分辨参数λ(r)来识别星系团中强引力透镜与弱引力透镜在质量重建可靠性上的径向转换，并验证了该参数能自然量化两种探针的相对可靠性，为联合重建提供了定量基础。","date":"2026-07-10","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.08286","score":85,"stars":4,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2607.11559","canonical_id":"2607.11559","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Can third- and fourth-order multipoles plus radial variation of iso-density ellipses explain the observed flux ratios in B1422$+$231? YES, and a lesson learned from a TNG100 lensing galaxy sample","authors":["Ruizhe Feng","Dandan Xu","Dominique Sluse","Giulia Despali","Anowar Shajib","Cai-Na Hao"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA","astro-ph.CO"],"summary":"本文以B1422+231系统为例，研究了来自TNG100模拟的非团块扰动（多极项m3、m4及q、φ_q的径向变化）如何解释强透镜类星体中的流量比异常。在较高观测精度下，平滑宏观模型（SIE+γ、EPL+γ）会产生位置和流量比异常，而加入这些扰动可有效解释异常现象。研究揭示了模型灵活性和简并性的重要教训。","date":"2026-07-14","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.11559","score":82,"stars":4,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2607.11675","canonical_id":"2607.11675","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Up, Up, and Away? Quantifying ISM Fallback using Ram Pressure Stripping Simulations","authors":["Harrison J. Souchereau","Stephanie Tonnesen","Jingyao Zhu","Jeffrey D. P. Kenney"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"本文通过流体动力学风洞模拟，研究了中等质量卫星星系在室女座星系团类似环境中受到冲压剥离时，冷星际介质的演化。研究发现即使气体最终会被完全剥离，冷气体仍会经历流出和回流（回退）的循环过程，回退在边缘-on风角时更为显著，主要发生在尾随侧象限，且大部分流入气体来自延伸到约20 kpc的“内尾”区域。论文还通过简单理想化模拟探讨了回退发生的可能原因，包括高倾角盘中的偏移旋转运动、盘遮挡和云增长等机制。","date":"2026-07-14","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.11675","score":66,"stars":3,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"galaxy gas","points":10}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Multi-phase and Molecular Gas","Dust and ISM"]},{"id":"2607.04959","canonical_id":"2607.04959","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Spectroscopic redshifts of selected flat-spectrum radio sources I","authors":["Dmitry Blinov","Alberto Floris","Andreas Zezas","Carolina Casadio","Elias Kyritsis","Valentina Missaglia","Vangelis Pantoulas","Avinash Kumar"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO","astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"SMILE项目首次光谱观测结果：为研究毫角秒尺度引力透镜系统，对约5000个射电源进行红移测量，发现491个源无红移数据，948个仅有测光红移且存在较大差异。本文报告了使用Skinakas 1.3米望远镜观测的15个目标中，6个新确定的光谱红移结果。","date":"2026-07-07","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.04959","score":65,"stars":3,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"gravitational lens modelling","points":28}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Other Selected Research"]},{"id":"2607.03430","canonical_id":"2607.03430","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Euclid: A UV-faint quasar in a highly luminous star-forming host galaxy at $z \\approx 7.7$","authors":["S. Belladitta","R. Decarli","E. Bañados","F. Walter","D. Yang","F. Guarneri","K. Jahnke","S. Bisogni","S. E. I. Bosman","X. Fan","Y. Fu","J. F. Hennawi","Y. Matsuoka","D. J. Mortlock","M. Onoue","J. -T. Schindler","L. Spinoglio","D. Stern","F. Wang","G. Vietri","C. J. Willott","J. Wolf","J. Yang","R. A. A. Bowler","K. I. Caputi","D. L. Clements","C. M. Gutierrez","H. J. A. Rottgering","D. Scott","F. Shankar","G. Zamorani","A. -C. Eilers","B. Altieri","S. Andreon","N. Auricchio","C. Baccigalupi","M. Baldi","A. Balestra","S. Bardelli","P. Battaglia","A. Biviano","M. Brescia","S. Camera","V. Capobi